data.text: @WalkerBragman Just wait till deaths aren't reported anymore. Or rather when deaths aren't reported by the MSM in any way that is visible and top of mind for most Americans. I guess that's already happening.

@Gurdur @h36_lexii @WalkerBragman Youre attributing the waves to different variants then? Omicron I’ll give you, but the timing of the waves between south and north Im sorry are simply inarguable.

@h36_lexii @DaveKapka @WalkerBragman Not only that, but COVID_19 is NOT a "seasonal" bug, as we understand seasonal pathogens. That was proven beyond all doubt in 2020/2021. Interesting ambiguity seen in the thread, tho
@DaveKapka @WalkerBragman @Gurdur But there was still a next worse season. That means COVID was not behind us abd it was not the time to open back up
